name: Gate Rusher
summary: Gate Rush VR", take control of a ball using a joystick to navigate through a series of gates in a vibrant virtual world. This VR game challenges your precision and timing as you twist and turn through different levels, each presenting unique obstacles and faster speeds. Experience the rush of making split-second maneuvers to pass through gates perfectly aligned with your trajectory. Perfect for players seeking an engaging VR experience with simple yet captivating gameplay mechanics.
